'''{{class|Actor}}'''
native bool '''StartConversation'''(Actor ''player'', bool ''faceTalker'' = true, bool ''saveAngle'' = true) {{git|92dbdd3}}
== Usage == Initializes a conversation between the caller and ''player''.
=== Parameters === *'''player''' :The player pawn which the caller is trying to start conversing with. *'''faceTalker''' :The caller and ''player'' be looking at each other while talking. *'''saveAngle''' :{{Moreinfo}}
=== Return value === Returns true if the caller initialized a conversation with the specified player, false otherwise.
